description.en-UK:
Imagine you had a fifty foot wingspan. Or indeed any wingspan. 
The NearBy scope is a bit like that, giving you an instant view of everything happening around you.

link_text.en-UK: See what's happening now with the Time Out scope

sub_description.en-UK: Need some fast night out recommendations? Check out all the options around you with TimeOut, one of the branded NearBy scopes.

description.en-UK: The Music scope lets you listen to music in your library, stream and download from the likes of Soundcloud and 7digital, or catch the latest gig with Songkick.

sub_description.en-UK: Runners need power tunes – fact. Soundcloud via the Music scope has you covered – fact.

description.en-UK: Interested in Sports, financial markets and the latest gossip? And it's never occured to you what a weird combination that is? Get the news that only you care about  with the News scope.

link_text.en-UK: Explore more News with the Euronews scope

sub_description.en-UK: The most watched European news channel is with us. Euronews is available 24/7 in 13 languages...or you could read it in one. Whichever you prefer!

description.en-UK: Kick start your day with all the essentials, including your reminders and tasks, recent messages and calls, weather updates and news headlines.

link_text.en-UK: Explore more Today with the branded Weather Channel scope

sub_description.en-UK: Rain. Shine. Storm...whatever the deal with the skies in your area, the Weather Channel has you covered. You'll never be with the wrong attire!

description.en-UK: Looking for culinary inspiration over the holidays? Our Food scope will satisfy all your gastronomy needs.
Festive trailers, reviews and listings are all right there at your fingertips in the Film scope, so you’ve got no excuse to bored over the holidays!
Bringing you the best of Bollywood all from within one screen. The Bollywood scope enables you to watch movies, listen to music and catch up on all the latest celeb gossip!
